==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsew
<hw>Un*sew"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>sew</ets>.]</ety> <def>To undo, as something sewn,
or something inclosed by sewing; to rip apart; to take out the stitches
of.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsex</ent>⟦br⟧
